    "long_instructions": "## Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Create a `Painter` object.\r\n2. Add methods to move the `Painter` to the cone.\r\n\t- **Hint:** Use your pseudocode on the activity guide for Task 1: A to B.\r\n    \r\n---\r\n###AI Tutor Support\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure how to create and move a Painter?**]\r\nAsk AI: \r\n- How do I create a `Painter` object in Python?\r\n- Which method makes the Painter move forward?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Stuck on getting to the cone?**]\r\nAsk AI:\r\n- How do I move the Painter multiple steps?\r\n- How do I get the Painter to turn around?\r\n:::\r\n",
